Underlying sources remain the property of their publishers:
- Philippine Statistics Authority (census, vital statistics, PSGC) — public
  government statistics.
- OpenHalalan (election vote counts) — see its CITATION.cff and license.
- English Wikipedia (2024 population transcription, pinned revision,
  verified against PSA totals) — CC BY-SA 4.0.
- faeldon/philippines-json-maps (boundary polygons, derived from PSA/NAMRIA).

Pipeline code (pipeline/*.py) is licensed under the MIT License.

